title: Aspen Ellis
text:
Welcome!
My name is Aspen Ellis - I’m a seabird conservation ecologist and a Ph.D. student at the University of California, Santa Cruz. My current research focuses on mitigation strategies for the impacts of offshore wind energy development to seabirds.



Education
PhD in Ecology & Evolutionary Biology (2021 - present) | University of California, Santa Cruz
BS in Environmental Science (2017) | University of Michigan
